Package it.polimi.ingsw.socket

package it.polimi.ingsw.socket
Shared package which contains the implementation for socket-to-socket communication protocol which will be used by both the client and the server.

Additionally, the it.polimi.ingsw.socket.packets subpackage contains all the possible packets that can be sent and received.
